nodes.text: A Banking Clan representative accompanied Chairman San Hill to visit the Quingarus Deluxe Droid Systems Factory.

During the Clone Wars, this man and Chairman San Hill visited Quingarus, threatening him with producing battle droids for them to pay off his debt. When he refused, the pair attacked him with a new model of battle droid, only being stopped by the intervention of Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi. The representatives fled the scene, but promised revenge if Quingarus didn't pay up.
